Description: Record 'asciicast' screencasts from R scripts. Convert them
    to animated SVG images, to be used in 'README' files, or blog posts.
    Includes 'asciinema-player' as an 'HTML' widget, and an 'asciicast'
    'knitr' engine, to embed 'ascii' screencasts in 'Rmarkdown' documents.
